---
import placeholder from "../assets/portfolio.png";
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="pt-10 pb-20 md:pt-16 md:pb-32 bg-white overflow-hidden"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-8 text-center lg:text-left">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight leading-tight"
          >
            Hola, soy <span class="text-indigo-600">Jeysonh Téllez</span>
          </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <span
              class="font-bold text-gray-900 border-b-4 border-indigo-100 italic"
              >Ingeniero en Sistemas</span
            > enfocado en el desarrollo <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold"
              >Full Stack</span
            >.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
            Cuento con una sólida base en <span class="font-bold text-gray-900"
              >Java (Spring Boot)</span
            > y ecosistemas modernos de JavaScript como <span
              class="font-bold text-gray-900">React y Angular</span
            >.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
            Tengo experiencia integrando soluciones de <span
              class="text-indigo-600 font-semibold">Machine Learning</span
            > en plataformas móviles y gestionando el ciclo de vida del software mediante
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Docker</span> y despliegues en
            plataformas <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">PaaS</span>.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl italic">
            Comprometido con la <span class="font-bold text-gray-700"
              >Clean Architecture</span
            >, los principios <span class="font-bold text-gray-700">SOLID</span> y
            la escritura de código escalable y eficiente.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4 pt-4">
          <a
            href="#projects"
            class="px-8 py-4 bg-gray-900 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-indigo-600 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo-100"
          >
            Ver Proyectos
          </a>
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-gray-900 border-2 border-gray-100 font-bold rounded-2xl hover:border-indigo-600 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            Contactar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-1 relative w-full max-w-md lg:max-w-none">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 rounded-3xl rotate-3 scale-105 -z-10 opacity-60"
        >
        </div>
        <img
          src={placeholder.src}
          alt="Jeysonh Téllez"
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-3xl relative z-10 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 object-cover aspect-square"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
